general.name: astraStarASPCAP
general.short: Results and best-fit models from the ASPCAP astra pipeline for a single star
general.description: Results and best-fit models from the ASPCAP astra pipeline for a single star. The ASPCAP flag bitmaps are documented at https://www.sdss.org/dr17/irspec/apogee-bitmasks#ParamBitMask, and the weights used when computing each abundance are documented at https://data.sdss5.org/sas/sdsswork/mwm/spectro/astra/component_data/aspcap/masks/
